title: Comedown Players of the Year
itunes:title: Comedown Players of the Year
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler are joined by Patrick Claybon to bringing you the latest news around the NFL including Aaron Rodgers lackluster beer chug (5:49), the Panthers signing Gerald McCoy (9:18), and Packers coach LaFleur coaching in a golf cart (13:18). We always talk about comeback players of the year, but what about players that had an impressive season last year that might be on the decline? The heroes list their comedown players of the year. (36:18)
